        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks RFA for extracts.</p>
            <p>Does not believe resemblances can be produced as RFA suggests, but would not deny that a strong mental shock may cause arrest of embryonic development and thus give rise to monstrosities.</p>
        </abstract>
