            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-8006.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from R. F. Albrecht, 13 October 1871</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD discussed the effects of maternal imagination on the foetus in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7951.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></ref> 2: 264.</note>
